。 2，咨询师对于来访者类型的偏好，在多大程度上会影响「无条件积极关注」这一大前提？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/607288452"}}, "attached_info": "ClUImpzqtau84pgsEAMaCDk3MjMzNTE0IOrSuqQGMAA4wQFAHnIJNjA3Mjg4NDUyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "31_1688011664.117018", "card_id": "Q_595603265", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 384}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么那么多人执着于考公务员呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-34510aef0115b37414467c5fa1a26316_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/595603265"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Impzqtau84pgsEAMaCDk0NjM3NjU2IKjP5KEGMAA4twRAH3IJNTk1NjAzMjY1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "32_1688011664.117664", "card_id": "Q_609288325", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 57}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "鲍威尔表示美联储预计会出现更多的紧缩力量，并重申「多数决策者预计今年将再加息两次」，释放了什么信号？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "每经 AI 快讯，6 月 28 日，美联储主席鲍威尔表示，美联储预计会出现更多的紧缩力量，美联储卷入限制区域的时间还不长，相信还会有更多的限制。并重申多数决策者预计今年将再加息两次。美联储主席鲍威尔表示，美联储预计会出现更多的紧缩力量 | 每经网美联储主席鲍威尔重申多数决策者预计今年将再加息两次 | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-b094449ca408ad20b915f7f71ac7bb72_720w.webp"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/609288325"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Impzqtau84pgsEAMaCDk3Njc4MTQ3IN+Q8aQGMAA4kQFAIHIJNjA5Mjg4MzI1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, 